{"tid":884013,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"佛像額上生出巨型「大痣」　原來係蜜蜂竇","createTime":"2018-10-31T09:31:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-31T14:43:14.000Z","uid":75969,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"f9ce2b9b3cbfdb883134304d51a35c718a031d56","tid":884013,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T09:31:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181031/photo/bkn-20181031120922195-1031_00952_001_03p.jpg?20181031123648\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20181031%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181031120922195-1031_00952_001_03p.jpg%3F20181031123648&h=ec490fa5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181031/photo/bkn-20181031120922195-1031_00952_001_02p.jpg?20181031123648\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20181031%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181031120922195-1031_00952_001_02p.jpg%3F20181031123648&h=6d6c6a82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日有網民在網上留言指，浙江杭州宋城景區一個巨型石雕佛像的額頭正中間，竟然生出了一個超巨大的蜜蜂竇，驟眼看還以為是「痣」。景區工作人員稱，這個蜜蜂竇已長了好幾年，因位於高處，處理難度大，故他們惟有「佛系」對待，不予理會。<br />\n<br />\n該網民指，日前和家人到宋城景區遊玩時，走到佛像下準備參拜祈福，誰知一抬頭發現佛像上有一塊巨大的斑點，拿相機放大來看，赫然是一個巨大蜂窩，上面還有蜜蜂飛來飛去。他們找上景區工作人員，建議盡快摘除蜂窩。<br />\n<br />\n工作人員就指，蜂窩從今年8月開始出現，且愈長愈大，但無力處理。有遊客覺得蜂窩帶來潛在風險，但有人就和工作人員一樣「佛系」，覺得不影響遊人安全的情況下也是一道風景。<br />\n<br />\n事件引起網友熱議，有網友笑說「佛祖長出美人啄了」，也有網友說「難道要在佛祖頭上殺生？」、「真會找地方，沒有人敢捅！」、「趕也趕不走的，可能是佛的旨意。」、「沒察覺到翻白眼的表情嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181031/bkn-20181031120922195-1031_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20181031%2Fbkn-20181031120922195-1031_00952_001.html&d=FwYAA6jDIqA0QZLQKYkRCp4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=718106b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181031/bkn-20181031120922195-1031_00952_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"8403ae71e6d512d2615a843c5b5cd7ffc7fa6784","tid":884013,"uid":34993,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T09:35:43.000Z","msg":"掃地恐傷螻蟻命"},{"pid":"5a1d28a5cc5789be4b55a3cdac0b312dc637bf3d","tid":884013,"uid":40903,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T09:36:14.000Z","msg":"家燕媽媽"},{"pid":"d1397ba5ec1ae62e62af832fde2c75f1d7610014","tid":884013,"uid":146243,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T09:37:07.000Z","msg":"個樣好無奈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2779822efe0de69c86c4a63ed6836d45d7acfcf1","tid":884013,"uid":208159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T09:37:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"29c3c96f206032512cc5f0f8d32ebbbac04274e7","tid":884013,"uid":167506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T10:00:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bf2117199f9195efc6a61ab0fa065b549c5d67d","tid":884013,"uid":103513,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T10:12:49.000Z","msg":"佛祖唔係本身就額頭有粒墨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n印象中見過啲圖片係有"},{"pid":"14d1dace2b3b01617d5ada9b4eddaddc01ca3d41","tid":884013,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T10:55:21.000Z","msg":"拎火箭炮轟佢落黎啦"},{"pid":"0bea6addf030fe5dd1dfebd7c12bf3812f7d638c","tid":884013,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0bf2117199f9195efc6a61ab0fa065b549c5d67d","tid":884013,"uid":103513,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T10:12:49.000Z","msg":"佛祖唔係本身就額頭有粒墨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n印象中見過啲圖片係有"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T11:04:10.000Z","msg":"印度果d可能係"},{"pid":"fc0ef4e056cb56126316b37ed6ecae82b3b8b934","tid":884013,"uid":182499,"like":4,"dislike":26,"score":-22,"quote":{"pid":"d1397